1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:05,960
The throne will be your doom!

2
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:18,000
Who is it?

3
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:20,120
It's me.

4
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:21,239
Thunder gave me nightmares.

5
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:22,400
I'm scared.

6
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,520
I'm scared too.

7
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:39,439
Does the thunder still scare you?

8
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:41,840
Not anymore.

9
00:00:46,407 --> 00:00:51,419
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

10
00:00:51,420 --> 00:00:56,019
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

11
00:00:56,020 --> 00:00:57,519
♪By your side once♪

12
00:00:57,520 --> 00:01:00,594
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

13
00:01:00,595 --> 00:01:04,569
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

14
00:01:04,570 --> 00:01:09,490
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

15
00:01:09,507 --> 00:01:14,219
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

16
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:18,781
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

17
00:01:18,782 --> 00:01:23,965
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

18
00:01:24,245 --> 00:01:26,606
=Shall We Dance=

19
00:01:26,607 --> 00:01:29,359
=Episode 6=

20
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:34,240
The throne will be your doom!

21
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,480
Who's there?

22
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,719
Shush.

23
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,840
It's me.

24
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,240
Thunder roars outside.

25
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,600
It gave me nightmares.

26
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,639
I'm scared.

27
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,000
Do mind your manners.

28
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,920
What you do here
is out of place.

29
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,559
I won't tell anyone.

30
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,959
This is our secret.

31
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,360
Just like when we were kids.

32
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,400
This goes against propriety.

33
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,000
I'm sleeping here tonight.

34
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,280
I'll sleep on the floor.

35
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,160
Forget it.

36
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,799
This is your room.

37
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,080
You take the bed.
I'll sleep on the floor.

38
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,600
Xiao Man,

39
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,520
your pillow smells great,

40
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,760
like a young lady's.

41
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,160
Your Majesty,

42
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,840
I should escort you back.

43
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,440
Why, Xiao Man?

44
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,800
Xiao Man...

45
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,000
Xiao Man...

46
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:08,839
Can we not

47
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,400
go back to
how we were as kids?

48
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:14,519
Are you still afraid of thunder now?

49
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,960
I'm not afraid anymore.

50
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,599
Ten years have passed.

51
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,440
We're no longer children.

52
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,560
We can't go back.

53
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,000
Never ever?

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,280
I don't believe that.

55
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,840
There must be a way for us to go back.

56
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,360
Look.

57
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,879
These are all my private clothes.

58
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,160
Pick one and change into it.

59
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,799
What for?

60
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,639
It's a secret for now.

61
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,520
Come on.

62
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,999
What are you doing?

63
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,239
Your Majesty can choose for me.

64
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,600
Anything will do.

65
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,200
Wait there.

66
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,960
How about these two?

67
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,360
We'll look like brothers in them.

68
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,040
Very well, little brother.

69
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,439
I'm taller than you now.

70
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:29,280
You should be calling me big brother.

71
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,120
I'll go change inside.

72
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,160
Why so bashful?

73
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,600
You're acting like a lady.

74
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,439
What a graceful, handsome youth.

75
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,079
Come,

76
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,279
I'll take you somewhere.

77
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,400
Where to?

78
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,880
(Yanbo Parlor.)

79
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,600
That was beautifully danced.

80
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,319
The performers here
are masters of their craft.

81
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,840
There are many skilled artists.

82
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,440
The music hall has its rules.

83
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,679
Honoured guests

84
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,279
may go to the private rooms upstairs

85
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:38,480
and invite a performer
for a solo display.

86
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,959
There are watchful eyes.

87
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,320
We must stay alert.

88
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,720
Do not lose yourself
in the stage performance.

89
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,559
I've truly broadened my horizons today.

90
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,439
When I return,

91
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,159
I shall build

92
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,559
a Yanbo Parlor of my own,

93
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,920
and gather artists from
across the land to entertain

94
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,920
and dance with me.

95
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,839
If you are pleased,

96
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,159
you may go to the upper floor

97
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,600
and invite that performer
to entertain you alone.

98
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,760
Very well.

99
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,000
Let's have a look.

100
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:08,999
Xiao Man,

101
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,359
let's go see for ourselves.

102
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,839
Come.

103
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,560
This way, please.

104
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:25,239
They say there is much
to enjoy within Yanbo Parlor.

105
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,560
Xiao Man, you must
make the most of it tonight.

106
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,680
I am Liu Mengmei, Young Master.

107
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:35,359
Your performance was truly splendid.

108
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,479
Any other specialty act?

109
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,120
My specialty is sword dancing.

110
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,639
Excellent.

111
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,640
I...

112
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,959
I would like to see a sword dance.

113
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,079
Please.

114
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:47,200
Then, forgive my humble display.

115
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,639
Excellent.

116
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,280
Your skill is indeed remarkable.

117
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,600
(He knows martial arts.)

118
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,080
Have you studied combat?

119
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,680
Only the bare basics.

120
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,560
(Test his skills.)

121
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,120
How about sparring with him?

122
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,360
I'm not a fighter.

123
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,520
Do not be alarmed, Young Master.

124
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,600
I am not Jing Ke the assassin,

125
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,520
nor am I Xiang Zhuang the warrior.

126
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,679
This young gentleman is
quite the handsome one.

127
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,240
You seem rather familiar.

128
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,040
Have you visited Yanbo Parlor before?

129
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,559
You do know how to flatter, sir.

130
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,680
No wonder so many are fond of you.

131
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:28,719
But I fear you've
mistaken me for someone else.

132
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,640
I have never been to Yanbo Parlor.

133
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,559
(He denies ever coming.)

134
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:38,079
This place is where many nobles

135
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,319
meet in secret.

136
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,960
Much has happened here.

137
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,280
Is that so?

138
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,360
Who, for instance?

139
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:46,319
For example,
the Imperial Prince Consort.

140
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,480
My uncle-in-law?

141
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:49,039
Well now...

142
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,799
Sneaking off to
amuse yourself behind Aunt's back.

143
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,000
Despicable.

144
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:55,679
There was also someone
who seemed a palace noble.

145
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,919
Others addressed him as

146
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,800
Director Jia.

147
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,360
Watch your tongue.

148
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,920
You are...

149
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,080
You too...

150
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,279
Splendid.

151
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,440
Utterly splendid.

152
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,160
What should we do next?

153
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,039
I've prepared a special game,

154
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:21,159
one only the two of us can play.

155
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,280
Alright.

156
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:26,720
Come with me.

157
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,120
You took me for Big Flower?

158
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,119
Stop following us.

159
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,480
We will be fine alone.

160
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,040
Slow down.

161
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,240
Xiao Man, slow down.

162
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,600
What exactly are we playing?

163
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,200
Slow down.

164
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:47,479
Play and fun.

165
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,439
That's all you think about!

166
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,439
Stand still.

167
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,880
I have something to tell you.

168
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:54,479
My swordsmanship outside
the palace was never perfected,

169
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,680
but I did master the ability
to remember anything at a glance.

170
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,120
And so?

171
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:02,280
So what exactly are we playing?

172
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,760
Dancing?

173
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,320
We'll play...

174
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,039
memorial recitation.

175
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,519
I can read the memorials submitted

176
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,359
to the Directorate of Ceremonial

177
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,560
before Director Jia takes them
and remember every word.

178
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:16,919
Now,

179
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,799
I'll recite them to you one by one.

180
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,359
Any loyal counsel or worthy advice,

181
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,519
you may take note of yourself,

182
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,520
so you may better grasp court affairs.

183
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,399
No!

184
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,319
I won't.

185
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,559
If you won't dance with me, fine,

186
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,799
but now you want me to work.

187
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,600
What if Director Jia scolds you?

188
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,279
Changes stir along the border.

189
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,880
Heavy troops must be deployed at once.

190
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,479
Guard against foreign powers,

191
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,160
whose ambitions are wolfish at heart.

192
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,880
(No need to test further.)

193
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,240
(Xiao Man is on my side.)

194
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,040
I'm glad.

195
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,759
I'm not saying this to please you.

196
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,119
But I am glad to hear that.

197
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,880
You're still my Xiao Man.

198
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,520
Xiao Man,

199
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,360
shall we dance?

200
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,839
Xiao Man.

201
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,040
Xiao Man?

202
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,479
Come on, Xiao Man.

203
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,680
Dance with me.

204
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,320
Xiao Man realised you're a woman?

205
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:24,520
And she still...

206
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,720
I won't spare her.

207
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,520
Sit down.

208
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,639
What's the hurry?

209
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:33,360
I haven't finished speaking.

210
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,479
So,

211
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:38,080
it would be one thing
if a fool like you failed to notice,

212
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,480
but don't tell me...

213
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,760
His Majesty didn't realise it either?

214
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,720
Realise what?

215
00:12:04,145 --> 00:12:08,065
♪I wanted to ask you
the meaning of forever♪

216
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:11,590
♪Is it longing that never rests♪

217
00:12:12,245 --> 00:12:15,502
♪Love that echoes without end♪

218
00:12:16,795 --> 00:12:20,390
♪Or promises that can't be kept♪

219
00:12:22,345 --> 00:12:25,765
♪All those vows of forever we made♪

220
00:12:26,307 --> 00:12:29,752
♪Are sealed away in darkness now♪

221
00:12:31,545 --> 00:12:34,352
♪How cruel♪

222
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:38,627
♪Love blooms and withers♪

223
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:43,159
♪The more I try to forget
the fiercer the love burns♪

224
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,280
(Xiao Man)

225
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,719
(is a girl...)

226
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:49,290
♪The more I retreat
the sharper it feels♪

227
00:12:49,657 --> 00:12:52,969
♪How am I supposed to let go♪

228
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:57,052
♪And bring this story to an end♪

229
00:12:59,007 --> 00:13:02,614
♪After ten thousand years
adrift in the mortal world♪

230
00:13:03,007 --> 00:13:07,152
♪Why is my wish still unfulfilled♪

231
00:13:07,219 --> 00:13:15,881
♪How absurd
that this longing just won't die♪

232
00:13:15,882 --> 00:13:20,894
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

233
00:13:20,895 --> 00:13:25,494
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

234
00:13:25,495 --> 00:13:26,994
♪By your side once♪

235
00:13:26,995 --> 00:13:30,069
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

236
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:34,044
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

237
00:13:34,045 --> 00:13:38,965
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

238
00:13:38,982 --> 00:13:43,727
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪
